      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a good start, really captures the atmosphere. To make the tension even more \"real\" for the audience, I need to ground it in the people living there. Can you expand on the scene by describing the types of people you'd see loitering on the corners or hanging out in front of those buildings? I want to make sure the reader understands exactly who makes this area feel so dangerous and unpredictable.",
